3           |4
<img src="images/Fusion3.jpg"  width= "100%"> Click on the upper surface inside  the part with the hole were the nut will be inserted. Go  with right click to "Create a new Sketch"  | <img src="../ConnectionParts/images/Fusion3.jpg"  width="100%"  > To make the whole body of hte connecting part invisible and just see the line of the surface, Go To " "Create" and click on "Project/Insert" and choose the surface.



